OpenSim::MovingMusclePoint

MovingMusclePoint Class Reference

#include <MovingMusclePoint.h>

Inheritance diagram for MovingMusclePoint:

List of all members.

Detailed Description

A class implementing a moving muscle point, which is a muscle point that moves in a body's reference frame as a function of a coordinate.

Author:
Peter Loan
Version:
1.0
